welcome_message_body: Welcome to Holly Hill, the charming city known for its beautiful parks and friendly community. We are excited to have you here and encourage you to explore and experience all that our city has to offer. Enjoy your stay!

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Daytona Beach International Airport serves both domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: North Terminal
terminals.description: The North Terminal at Daytona Beach International Airport is primarily used for regional and commuter flights.

wifi.note: Passengers can connect to the airport's free WiFi network for up to 2 hours per day.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: This is the main terminal of New Smyrna Beach Municipal Airport, serving domestic flights.

wifi.note: Free wifi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Bunnell Flagler County Airport serves all commercial and private flights.

terminals.name: Private Terminal
terminals.description: The private terminal at Bunnell Flagler County Airport caters to private and chartered flights.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.
